        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Powerful Image Editing Suite",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " means you do not have to export to Photoshop for basic fixes. Inpainting, outpainting, upscaling, and background removal all happen inside the platform. I have finished entire pieces without leaving the browser.",
